#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.29"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.29:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.29:0.2"
msgid "3. Bhāravagga"
msgstr "3. The Burden"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.29:0.3"
msgid "29. Abhinandanasutta"
msgstr "29. Taking Pleasure"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.29:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.2"
msgid "“Yo, bhikkhave, rūpaṃ abhinandati, dukkhaṃ so abhinandati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, if you take pleasure in form, you take pleasure in suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.3"
msgid "Yo dukkhaṃ abhinandati, aparimutto so dukkhasmāti vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"If you take pleasure in suffering, I say you’re not exempt from suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.4"
msgid "Yo vedanaṃ abhinandati …"
msgstr "If you take pleasure in feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.5"
msgid "yo saññaṃ abhinandati …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.6"
msgid "yo saṅkhāre abhinandati …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.7"
msgid "yo viññāṇaṃ abhinandati, dukkhaṃ so abhinandati."
msgstr "consciousness, you take pleasure in suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.8"
msgid "Yo dukkhaṃ abhinandati, aparimutto so dukkhasmāti vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"If you take pleasure in suffering, I say you’re not exempt from suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.9"
msgid "Yo ca kho, bhikkhave, rūpaṃ nābhinandati, dukkhaṃ so nābhinandati."
msgstr ""
"If you don’t take pleasure in form, you don’t take pleasure in suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.10"
msgid "Yo dukkhaṃ nābhinandati, parimutto so dukkhasmāti vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"If you don’t take pleasure in suffering, I say you’re exempt from suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.11"
msgid "Yo vedanaṃ nābhinandati …"
msgstr "If you don’t take pleasure in feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.12"
msgid "yo saññaṃ nābhinandati …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.13"
msgid "yo saṅkhāre nābhinandati …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.14"
msgid "yo viññāṇaṃ nābhinandati, dukkhaṃ so nābhinandati."
msgstr "consciousness, you don’t take pleasure in suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.29:1.15"
msgid "Yo dukkhaṃ nābhinandati, parimutto so dukkhasmāti vadāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"If you don’t take pleasure in suffering, I say you’re exempt from suffering.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.29:1.16"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
